giving @math{zeta=[0.0,0.0,1.0,1.0]} and 
@math{G(z_1,z_2,z_3,z_4)=[z_1, z_3, z_1, z_4-0.3*z_3+0.7]}

Note that @var{x} is not an argument of function @var{G}.  The 
